<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="sec-equazione" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Equazione della retta</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>Intro to section, because we will have subsections.</p>
    <p>Another paragraph of the introduction.</p>
  </introduction>

  <subsection xml:id="subsec-a-subsection">
    <title>Teoremi e dimostrazioni</title>
    <p>Content of the subsection.</p>
    <p>More content.</p>

    <theorem xml:id="thm-derivazione_retta">
      <title>Equazione della retta passante per l'origine</title>
      <statement>
        <p>Le rette che passano per l'origine hanno equazione esplicita <m>y=mx</m> con <m>m\in\R</m>.</p>
      </statement>
      <proof>
        <sidebyside widths='35% 60%' valign='middle'>
          <image><latex-image>
            \begin{tikzpicture}
            \begin{axis}
            \addplot[funzione principale, domain=-3:3] {.7*x};
            \end{axis}
            \end{tikzpicture}
          </latex-image></image>
          <p>Dimostrazione ...</p>
        </sidebyside>
      </proof>
      </theorem>
  </subsection>


  <conclusion>
    <p>
      After the last subsection, you might have a conclusion.
    </p>
  </conclusion>
</section>

